              Signup for our newsletter to get half off your first session
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="email-popup-text-section px-4 py-3">
            <div class="mb-4 text-center email-signup-form">
              <div class="klaviyo-form-Yvf79G"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="email-popup-fine-print">
